description: With pre-chopped, pre-marinated ingredients, our new Fresh & Fast recipes are on the table in just 15 minutes. Perfect for busy weeknights - and busy people. This week, enjoy tender beef strips in a sweet and savoury char siu sauce, served with flat noodles and colourful veggies.

*Heads-up - you'll need a microwave for this recipe.*
